Package: simplepicture
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight cross-platform image viewer
 A fast and lightweight image viewer built with Qt 5.
 Supports PNG, JPG, BMP, GIF, WEBP, TIFF, ICO, SVG formats.
 Features mouse wheel zoom and keyboard navigation.
